  description:
    English: After assisting (dealing 70% of the damage to the enemy) or successfully
      killing an enemy, the entity will enter a rage state for 3 seconds. In this
      state, its movement speed and attack speed are increased by 70%.
    Vietnamese: "Sau khi h\u1ED7 tr\u1EE3(s\xE1t th\u01B0\u01A1ng g\xE2y l\xEAn k\u1EBB
      \u0111\u1ECBch chi\u1EBFm 70%) ho\u1EB7c gi\u1EBFt th\xE0nh c\xF4ng m\u1ED9t
      k\u1EBB \u0111\u1ECBch, th\u1EF1c th\u1EC3 s\u1EBD r\u01A1i v\xE0o c\u01A1n
      cu\u1ED3ng n\u1ED9 trong 3 gi\xE2y. Trong tr\u1EA1ng th\xE1i n\xE0y, n\xF3
      \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\u0103ng 70% t\u1ED1c ch\u1EA1y ch\xF9ng 70% t\u1ED1c
      \u0111\xE1nh"
